reviewText: The stories were good and enjoying Jimmy Stewart in the movies I was not disappointed with these earlier stories on CD.
Great show - heard one on Sirius and immediately wanted the whole series.  Glad to find it here.
love to listen to the oldies! great product!
When busy working on computer, doing desk work or driving in the car, old time radio is just the ticket.

This is an excellent CD (MP3 format) on one of the Old Time Radio Shows, The Six Shooter.
The quality is very good.
Hearing the voice of Jimmy Stewart is great.
This was a good purchase and I would certainly purchase more from this seller.
I listen to these old time radio shows as I workout in the gym.
